when Mexico

00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:34.800
does impose a notice as of April 20

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:36.440
to ours,

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:39.720
it must be said that the decision seems to be well thought out.

00:00:40.080 --> 00:00:40.880
and smart,

00:00:41.240 --> 00:00:42.840
because they are the tourism unions

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:45.280
