00:00:48.360 --> 00:00:53.120
76,300 have visited our country in 2,023.

00:00:53.360 --> 00:00:56.160
More Mexicans have arrived in Peru than France,

00:00:56.240 --> 00:00:58.000
Canada and the United Kingdom.

00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:01.240
